.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>The ‘first&nbsp;released’ dataset stores the original HICP data as&nbsp;released&nbsp;on the official publication dates (non-revised). It includes the full set of indices and monthly and annual rates of change for all geographical entities (aggregates and countries). This dataset is compiled according to the European Classification of&nbsp;Individual&nbsp;Consumption According to Purpose (ECOICOP) ver. 2, available in base years&nbsp;2025=100 and 2015=100.</p><p>As a result of a technical error, the “first released data” dataset [prc_hicp_fpd] for January 2026 published on 25 February 2026 was updated on 3 March 2026.</p><p>The “first released data” published on 25 February 2026 are available&nbsp;<a href=\"https://circabc.europa.eu/ui/group/7b031f10-ac19-4da3-a36f-58708a70133d/library/18632f8f-5c92-4330-95d0-ef25240b44d6\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></p><p><br></p>","id":"PRC_HICP_FPD","agencyId":"ESTAT","version":"1.0","datastructure":{"id":"PRC_HICP_FPD","agencyId":"ESTAT","version":"15.0"},"annotation":[{"type":"CREATED","date":"2026-01-27T09:31:02+0100"},{"type":"DISSEMINATION_DOI_XML","title":"<adms:identifier xmlns:adms=\"http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#\" xmlns:skos=\"http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core.html\" xmlns:dct=\"http://purl.org/dc/terms/\" xmlns:rdf=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#\"><adms:Identifier rdf:about=\"https://doi.org/10.2908/PRC_HICP_FPD\"><skos:notation rdf:datatype=\"http://purl.org/spar/datacite/doi\">10.2908/PRC_HICP_FPD</skos:notation><dct:creator rdf:resource=\"http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/ESTAT\"/><dct:issued rdf:datatype=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date\">2026-01-27</dct:issued></adms:Identifier></adms:identifier>"},{"type":"DISSEMINATION_EXPLANATORY_LINK","title":"text-category","href":"https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/databrowser-backend/api/public/explanatory-notes/get/Info_note_HICP_COICOP18_20260128.pdf","text":"Information note"},{"